      _TV Show Notes_ 
      ===============----------------------------------------------------
                                   
       Inexperienced skipper Chaz Bruce and his crew run into difficulty 
       when a rope wraps around the boat's propeller and the engine 
       loses revs, but he is determined to prove himself. Meanwhile, 
       disaster strikes for Jimmy Buchan, and captain Alan Watt heads
       for the North Atlantic

